          ¿Interesado en trabajar conmigo?
        </h3>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Estoy disponible para proyectos freelance y oportunidades laborales
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a 
            href="/assets/cv/Josue-Flores-CV.pdf" 
            download="Josue-Flores-CV.pdf"
            class="group bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 hover:from-blue-700 hover:to-purple-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl flex items-center justify-center gap-3"
          >
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:animate-bounce" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 17a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1zm3.293-7.707a1 1 0 011.414 0L9 10.586V3a1 1 0 112 0v7.586l1.293-1.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-3 3a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-3-3a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
